lueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011849, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "It is recommended to say the following dua <Allahumma haazehil ayyaamul>, which is reported by Shaykh Tusi and Sayyid Ibn Tawus from Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a), after the Fajr namaz and before Maghrib namaz, ie. from the 1st of Zil-Hijjah to the eve of 9th Zil-Hijjah (Night of Arafat).", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mustahab hai keh dua <Allahumma haazehil ayyaamul> ko, jo Shaikh Tusi aur Sayyed ibne Tawus ne Imam Sadiq (a) se riwaayat ki hai keh, namaz-e-Fajr ke baad aur namaz-e-Maghrib se pehle, 1st Zilhijjah se 9th Zilhijjah ki shab (yaane Shab-e-Arafat) tak padhe.", "UrduDescription": "پہلے دن سے عرفہ کے دن تک نمازِ فجر کے بعد اور نمازِمغرب سے پہلے دُعا <اَللّٰهُمَّ هٰذِهِ الْاَيَّامُ> پڑھے ؛ جو شیخؒ و سیدؒ نے امام جعفر صادق ؑسے نقل کی ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, 